Last Updated: August 2023
Our privacy policy is designed to provide transparency into our privacy practices and principles, in a format that our guests can navigate, read, and understand. HyperBeard, Inc. and its subsidiaries (collectively, “HyperBeard”) is dedicated to treating your personal information with care and respect.
This privacy policy describes how HyperBeard collects, uses, and discloses information from players of its games (“HyperBeard Games”). Please read this privacy policy carefully so that you understand our information practices. By downloading, accessing, and/or playing the HyperBeard Games, you consent to the collection of information about you, pursuant to this privacy policy.
If you are a California resident, additional privacy terms set out in
Appendix A
also apply to the processing of information collected in the course of your playing the games.
If you are located in the European Economic Area or the UK, additional privacy terms set out in
Appendix B
also apply to the processing of your personal information.
If you are using our services through a game on Apple Arcade, please see our Apple Arcade specific privacy policy
here
.
